  "body": "<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><img src=\"https://v.blakesmods.com/banners/mysticalautomation?source=modrinth\" width=\"840\" height=\"168\"></span></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/mystical-agriculture\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img src=\"https://blakesmods.com/img/banner/mysticalagriculture_required.png\" width=\"840\" height=\"92\"></a></p>\n<p style=\"display: flex;\"><a style=\"margin-right: 8px;\" href=\"https://blakesmods.com/mystical-automation\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"> <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/endpoint?url=https://api.blakesmods.com/v2/badges/mysticalautomation/downloads&amp;style=for-the-badge\"> </a> <a style=\"margin-right: 8px;\" href=\"https://blakesmods.com/mystical-automation\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"> <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/endpoint?url=https://api.blakesmods.com/v2/badges/mysticalautomation/version&amp;style=for-the-badge\"> </a> <a style=\"margin-right: 8px;\" href=\"https://blakesmods.com/mystical-automation\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"> <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/endpoint?url=https://api.blakesmods.com/v2/badges/mysticalautomation/mc_version&amp;style=for-the-badge\"> </a> <a style=\"margin-right: 8px;\" href=\"https://blakesmods.com/docs/mysticalautomation\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"> <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=docs&amp;message=view&amp;color=brightgreen&amp;style=for-the-badge\"> </a> <a href=\"https://blakesmods.com/wiki/mysticalautomation\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"> <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=wiki&amp;message=view&amp;color=brightgreen&amp;style=for-the-badge\"> </a></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">This mod adds additional content to&nbsp;<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/mystical-agriculture\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Mystical Agriculture.</a></span></p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><strong>Features</strong></span></h2>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Infuser:</strong> Automatically infuse Essences using Infusion Crystals.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Crafter:</strong> Automatically craft regular crafting recipes.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Farmer:</strong> Automatically grow and harvest crops in a single block.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Fertilizer:</strong> Automatically apply fertilizers like Fertilized Essence or Bone Meal to a field of crops.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Infusion/Awakening Altarnators:</strong> Automatically craft Infusion/Awakening Altar recipes with a single block.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Enchanternator:</strong> Automatically apply enchantments to items.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><a href=\"https://bisecthosting.com/blakesmods\"><strong><img src=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/partners/custom-banners/fdf1b29a-987b-450e-b6d4-a16c2da8aadf.png\" width=\"1086\" height=\"170\"></strong></a></span></p>",
